Hello everyone! Virtuosys.blogspot.com is back!
After 7-month period break, we’re returning in the attempt to bring along some musical reviews, rock hints and in the meanwhile, sort of metaphysical discussions.
You may notice we are reporting in English now, in order to reach a wider spread.
